Package com.intellij.execution.process

Interface ProcessOutputTypes


  • public interface ProcessOutputTypes

    • Field Summary

      Fields 
      Modifier and Type Field and Description
      static Key<?> STDERR
      Please use ProcessOutputType.STDERR instead.
      static Key<?> STDOUT
      Please use ProcessOutputType.STDOUT instead.
      static Key<?> SYSTEM
      Please use ProcessOutputType.SYSTEM instead.

    • Field Detail

      • SYSTEM

        static final Key<?> SYSTEM
        Please use ProcessOutputType.SYSTEM instead.

      • STDOUT

        static final Key<?> STDOUT
        Please use ProcessOutputType.STDOUT instead. Represents process standard output stream.

        Please note that stdout colored output type doesn't equal to this instance: use 

         ProcessOutputType.isStdout(key)
        instead of 
         ProcessOutputTypes.STDOUT.equals(key) or ProcessOutputTypes.STDOUT == key

      • STDERR

        static final Key<?> STDERR
        Please use ProcessOutputType.STDERR instead. Represents process standard error stream.

        Please note that stderr colored output type doesn't equal to this instance: use 

         ProcessOutputType.isStderr(key)
        instead of 
         ProcessOutputTypes.STDERR.equals(key) or ProcessOutputTypes.STDERR == key
